Interface Summary
Message Interface for messages to send over network
 

Class Summary
Auction Saves important data for an auction
AuctionEvent Class wich contains the Constructor and all getters and setters for the specific EventType for Autions
BidEvent Class wich contains the Constructor and all getters and setters for the specific EventType for Bids
BidMessage MEssage which is sent when user bids
Bill Provides the Bills for the BillingServer
CreateMessage Message which is send, when user Creates an auction
DataManager Manages the auctions and everything who needs to needs to be stored
Event Provides the basic Event which the specific Events can extend from
ListMessage Message which is send when User lists auctions
LoginMessage Message which is send when user logs in
LogoutMessage Message which is send when user logs out
PriceStep Provides the Basic Model for a PriceStep which is created at the BillingServer
PriceSteps Provides the Methods to create delete and printing out a PriceStep which is created at the BillingServer
Properties This Class gets a Path as parameter. this path directs to the specific properties file to check login data or something else
StatisticsEvent Provides Methods to create and printing out StatisticsEvents
User Represents a user and all his important data
UserEvent Class wich contains the Constructor and all getters and setters for the specific EventType for Bids
 

Enum Summary
EventType Provides all types of Events which can occur as EnumTypes
